OL,3,CGym, cinema and sauna: Life on 'hotel'
OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,FITV Calendar reporter Jonathan Brown
OL,7,Fspent the day on the Rough gas storage
OL,8,Ffacility, 18 miles off the Yorkshire
OL,9,Fcoast, where there are plans to adapt
OL,10,Fto provide fuel for years to come.
OL,12,FWith 100 staff working on rotation, a
OL,13,Frestaurant, a gym, a sauna and a
OL,14,Fcinema it's easy to see why those who
OL,15,Frun it call it the "hotel".
OL,17,FBut this is far from your average
OL,18,Fholiday retreat.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
