OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,FOnly accessible by helicopter, the
OL,7,FRough gas storage facility is a huge
OL,8,Fplatform in the middle of the North
OL,9,FSea managing the flow of natural gas
OL,10,Ffrom a vast cavern of porous rock
OL,11,F2.7km beneath the water's surface to
OL,12,Fthe Yorkshire coast 18 miles away.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
