OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,FI was given special access to hear
OL,7,Fabout plans to create a similar site
OL,8,Ffor hydrogen, which could see Rough's
OL,9,Funderground storage system used for a
OL,10,Fdifferent fuel in decades to come. But
OL,11,FI was equally keen to find out what
OL,12,Flife at sea is like on board a
OL,13,Ffacility that even those with
OL,14,Frelatives who work there rarely
OL,15,Fexperience firsthand.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
