OL,3,CGym, cinema and sauna: Life on 'hotel'
OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,FAs the helicopter becomes airborne to
OL,7,Fbegin its journey from Humberside
OL,8,FAirport to Rough, the views over the
OL,9,FHumber are a taster of the vistas to
OL,10,Fcome. You hover over wind farms as
OL,11,Fyour landing spot appears in the
OL,12,Fdistance.
OL,14,FThe flight itself is a mere 20
OL,15,Fminutes, but once on board the
OL,16,Fplatform, it feels like the most
OL,17,Fremote location on earth.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
