OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,FStaff work 14 days straight - 12 hours
OL,7,Fa day - so the platform has to
OL,8,Ffunction as a home as well as a
OL,9,Fworkplace.
OL,11,FJon Wason, who is in charge of
OL,12,Fcatering on board, says the restaurant
OL,13,Ftries to provide as varied a menu as
OL,14,Fpossible.
OL,16,F"We do a roast of the day and filled
OL,17,Fbaguettes and things like that and
OL,18,Fthere's always fish on twice a day and
OL,19,Fthen night times we do spicier
OL,20,Fthings," he says.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
