OL,3,CGym, cinema and sauna: Life on 'hotel'
OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,F"They got really good selection. We
OL,7,Fdon't charge the prices the
OL,8,Frestaurants charge, but we sell with
OL,9,Fthe ingredients we got. We try and
OL,10,Fmake it as nice as we can."
OL,12,FIt's important, he says, that staff
OL,13,Fare able to enjoy their down time.
OL,15,F"You haven't got much to look forward
OL,16,Fto when you're finished, right?" he
OL,17,Fsays.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
