OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F367A1732648965
OL,3,CGym, cinema and sauna: Life on 'hotel'
OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,F"Maybe phoning your loved ones,
OL,7,Fwatching telly and your food so you've
OL,8,Fgot to try and make sure the food's as
OL,9,Fgood as you can."
OL,11,FAnd it gets good reviews from the
OL,12,Fcustomers it serves.
OL,14,FOperation superintendent Dave Burnett
OL,15,Ftells me: "The food is awesome, it's
OL,16,Fpretty good I can't complain. I'm
OL,17,Fgoing to be on at Christmas this year
OL,18,Fand Christmas is usually pretty good."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
