OL,3,CGym, cinema and sauna: Life on 'hotel'
OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,FDave is part of a vast engineering
OL,7,Foperation that doesn't stop for life
OL,8,Fevents on dry land - his young
OL,9,Fdaughter and heavily pregnant wife are
OL,10,Fwaiting at home.
OL,12,FIn the meantime, he and his colleagues
OL,13,Fbunk two to a room.
OL,15,F"It comes with some real positives,
OL,16,Fbut it also comes with some some
OL,17,Fnegatives," he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
