OL,3,CGym, cinema and sauna: Life on 'hotel'
OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,F"I've got a daughter, Phoebe, who's
OL,7,Fseven, so we've got to come up with
OL,8,Fsome imaginative ways over the years
OL,9,Fto kind of convince her that I'm home
OL,10,Ffor Christmas. That can be quite
OL,11,Fdifficult. I've got another child on
OL,12,Fthe way in January as well - a little
OL,13,Fboy. So it's always the lottery of
OL,14,Fmaking sure that I'm going to be home
OL,15,Ffor when the baby's due.
OL,17,F"That can be a little bit nerve
OL,18,Fwracking, but fingers crossed the
OL,19,Fdecks line up and it'll be okay."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
