OL,3,CGym, cinema and sauna: Life on 'hotel'
OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,FZoe Long is the platform's own medic -
OL,7,Fthe only woman among 100 men.
OL,9,F"I was an NHS paramedic for 16 years,"
OL,10,Fshe says. "And then I decided I wanted
OL,11,Fto go into, like, remote and offshore.
OL,13,F"You kind of have to think out of the
OL,14,Fbox a little bit more. And how are you
OL,15,Fgoing to keep someone alive whilst
OL,16,Fwaiting for a helicopter."
OL,18,FZoe has dealt with broken bones and
OL,19,Feven heart attacks.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
