OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F367A1732648965
OL,3,CGym, cinema and sauna: Life on 'hotel'
OL,4,Cgas platform 18 miles offshore
OL,6,F"When I tell people I'm the only woman
OL,7,Fhere with 100 guys they're like what
OL,8,F'why would you do that?' But it's like
OL,9,Fhaving 100 brothers it's nice.
OL,11,F"I quite like being in the middle of
OL,12,Fthe sea. Sometimes we get some crazy
OL,13,Fweather here and, and it feels very
OL,14,Fwild. And other days it can be
OL,15,Fcompletely flat calm and there's
OL,16,Fdolphins and seals going past."
OL,18,FSo while it stands alone - stranded
OL,19,Fmiles from civilisation - this
OL,20,Funorthodox outpost offers a way of
OL,21,Flife few ever get to experience.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/12
